{"tid":1084470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 賀！網民高呼要退貨：「我是為了 AirPower 才買 AirPods 2 無線版！」","createTime":"2019-03-30T12:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T13:26:48.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6d92769a1b58edc537e01169b93ccbfbb10cf70d","tid":1084470,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:12:06.000Z","msg":"今天，蘋果宣佈 AirPower 無線充電板要叫停，引來大量網民的熱烈討論。早前 AirPods 第二代正式開售時，提供了無線充電版及非無線充電版供選擇，很多人為了要配 AirPower 才選購無線充電版。而當中更有不少人預計 AirPower 即將發售，所以才選購 AirPods 2 無線充電版。<br />\n<br />\n現在，不少已買無線充電版 AirPods 2 的網民卻感到「受騙」，揚言控告蘋果違反「商品說明條例」。更有網民笑言他是為了 AirPower 才買 iPhone X 的！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/03/30/airpods2-wireless-airpower/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2019%2F03%2F30%2Fairpods2-wireless-airpower%2F&d=Ru8OiKpQtXbNv5YRwinC6i2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=11311e9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/03/30/airpods2-wireless-airpower/</a>"},{"pid":"f25915221b1c2d9241f47d359ccb5a8b22cbfd6e","tid":1084470,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:12:18.000Z","msg":"apple rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1867acfeba5c01beae21b8f994566fb1ae652536","tid":1084470,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a40f50a01ef21f6de25af13c69e6ea79aa98270","tid":1084470,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1351e4c4934e5c67d64e5fb4614fa2076e6f9c","tid":1084470,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim